research_municipality_step.notes: As of May 21, 2025, the former mayor, Mark Wood, did not run for re-election. The newly elected mayor, Rich Booth, declined the position, and Mayor Pro Tem Mel Basham was not serving. Council members Gary Wulf and Matt Smith were maintaining city operations. Based on term expiration dates from May 2025, Aldermen for Place 1, 2, and 3 have terms expiring in May 2026, while Aldermen for Place 4 and 5 had terms expiring in May 2025. Therefore, there is no currently seated Mayor or Mayor Pro Tem, and the listed Aldermen are the active elected officials.
